        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【報價】Porsche Design Honor Magic V2 RSR 國行抵港速試　手感超佳 + 機身超有型</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/26/honor-magic-v2-rsr-porsche-design-china-ver-in-hk/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=honor-magic-v2-rsr-porsche-design-china-ver-in-hk</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/26/honor-magic-v2-rsr-porsche-design-china-ver-in-hk/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Edward]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 13:20:44 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[honor]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Magic V2]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[porsche design]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[RSR]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1221599</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>之前我們都為大家提及過，Huawei 已宣佈正式與 Porsche Design 結束合作關係，而後者現在就改為與 Honor 合作，而最近他們推出的 Porsche Design Honor Magic V2 RSR 國行「大摺」就迅速引入香港市場，究竟這部稱為「波子」牌頭首部摺機初步玩起來手感如何？就讓 Edward 帶大家去看看，並同時為大家報導它的定價吧。</p><h2>超型格外形 + 鈦合金手感鉸位</h2><p>今次 Honor 與 Porsche Design 合作推出的這部 Magic V2 RSR（下文簡稱 V2 RSR），基本來説機身佈局與一般版的 Magic V2 是幾乎相同的，不過 V2 RSR 的機背雖然仍是採用玻璃物料，但所採用的 Agate Grey 深灰色配色加上磨砂工藝後無論看還是摸上去也很有金屬感。此外，它的機背中央亦加入了微微拱起的線條，類似模擬 Porsche 車身的 Flyline 設計，令這部特別版「大摺」很有 Porsche 名跑的感覺。至於鉸位方面，雖然仍然採用金屬物料製造，但外表的磨砂令它很像鈦合金物料的手感，配合機背設計，摸上手對手感有很大提升。此外，它的相機模組亦比一般版更加大亦更加有型，整體看起來設計很有心思。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221602" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155813-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155813-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155813.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲V2 RSR 的機背雖然仍是用上強化玻璃物料，但就加入磨砂工藝，所以無論看起來還是摸上手，金屬感亦十分明顯，另外，磨砂設計亦令機背不易留下指紋，使用體驗更佳。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221603" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155818-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155818-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155818.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲機背中央凸起了一條線，模擬 Porsche 超跑流線型車身的設計，型格十足。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221604" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155828-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155828-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155828.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而 V2 RSR 的相機模組不但變大了很多，也是模仿 Porsche 跑車的溜背舷窗，令手機設計極具超跑感。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221605" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_160445-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_160445-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_160445.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至於機身鉸位用料上，V2 RSR（上）與一般版 Magic V2（下）也有不同，看起來十分相似，但摸上手 V2 RSR 的鉸位外殼更像時下流行的鈦合金物料。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221606" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155953-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155953-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155953.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲加上 V2 RSR 仍然保留了一般版 Magic V2 的輕薄設計，所以作為 Porsche Design 推出的第一部摺機，V2 RSR 真的做得十分出色，上手使用手感亦是上佳。</p><h2>包裝附送機套觸控筆</h2><p>此外，Honor V2 RSR 的包裝亦十分有心思，不但附送超美的真皮手機背蓋，亦附送一般版沒有的 Honor 觸控筆，就連筆亦設有獨立外攜盒方便大家帶出街使用。而作為超跑特別版的「大摺」，V2 RSR 亦有附送車充，而車充與手機本身的充電器也同樣支援 66W 有線快充，這個配套及設計也可見出廠商超有心思。至於硬件方面，大致上與 Magic V2 一般版差不多，同樣是內建了 Qualcomm Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 處理器、16GB RAM、6.43 吋 2376 x 1060 解像度 120Hz 更新率外熒幕、7.92 吋 2344 x 2156 解像度 120Hz 更新率可摺式內熒幕、3 鏡式主相機（5,000 萬像素主攝 + 5,000 萬像素超廣角 + 2,000 萬像素遠攝）及 5,000mAh 容量電池，不過 V2 RSR 就有提供 1TB 容量的內存，對用家來説應該十分夠用了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221607" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155400-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155400-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155400.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲V2 RSR 隨機是附送 Honor 自家的觸控筆，與一般版十分不同（一般版是需要另購的）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221608" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155714-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155714-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155714.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲不只送筆，隨機亦附送觸控筆的外攜盒，十分細心。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221609" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155705-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155705-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155705.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而且無論是手機背及鉸位保護蓋，還是觸控筆外攜盒，也是採用真皮物料製造，設計十分用心。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221610" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155442-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155442-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155442.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221611" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155525-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155525-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155525.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Honor 另一個細心之處，就是附送的充電火牛除了有一般的 66W 快充火牛外，還為有車一族附送同樣支援 66W 有線快充的車充。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221612" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155950-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155950-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155950.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221613" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_160005-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_160005-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_160005.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲V2 RSR 的外熒幕及內熒幕，與一般版相同，同樣分別是 6.43 吋及 7.92 吋。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221614" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_160321-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_160321-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_160321.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲熒幕依然支援 120Hz 更新率，顯示效果仍然十分理想。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221615" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_160058-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_160058-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_160058.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲不過介面上某程預載程式就換上了 Porsche Design 風格的圖示，令機身內外設計歸於統一。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221616" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_160042-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_160042-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_160042.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲硬件配置大致與一般版 Magic V2 相同，不過它的內存就增大至 1TB，對用家來説應該十分夠用。</p><p>至於定價方面，香港店舖開價為 $18,800，其實也只是比國內開價貴了千多元而已，而且以這部奢華超跑「大摺」來説，開價亦算合理。對「波子」版手機有愛的用家，不妨考慮一下？</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221617" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155322-1-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155322-1-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155322-1.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><strong>售價：$18,800</strong><br /><strong>查詢：三禾電氣（6838 1001）</strong><br /><b>相關文章:</b></p><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/01/honor-v-purse-china-version-review/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】HONOR V Purse 國行　外形　手感　折疊功能　熒幕　相機　效能開箱評測</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/25/huawei-porsche-design-partnership/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">華為與 Porsche Design 合作告終　改與榮耀品牌合作</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/12/honor-magic-v2-announce-in-hk/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【報價】Honor 2 代摺機 Magic V2 港行正式推出　定價進取 + 預訂禮品吸引</a></li></blockquote><p></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/26/honor-magic-v2-rsr-porsche-design-china-ver-in-hk/mobile-phone/">【報價】Porsche Design Honor Magic V2 RSR 國行抵港速試　手感超佳 + 機身超有型</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
